SELECT * FROM hotels WHERE city = 'Copenhagen' AND country = 'DK' AND stars <= 3 AND (parking = 'free' OR wifi = 'free') AND (pool = 1 OR beach_access IN ('private beach', 'beach access') OR child_pool = 1) AND playground = 1;
